data.description: Country Roads, Take you home.  Welcome to the true essence of farmhouse living, with a convenient location to the Granbury town center! The perfect blend of rural serenity and urban amenities.  This property is situated on a desirable 7.5 acre plot, completely fenced in, and includes a 1,000 sqft Guest House with 2 bedrooms, a full bathroom, kitchen, and living space which is ideal for your family or guests.  This also presents PRIME AirBNB, VRBO, or Long-Term Rental potential!  The main home embodies both luxury and comfort that boasts a versatile layout.  5 Bedrooms. Perfect for both relaxation and entertainment.  Recent upgrades include new flooring, appliances, tankless water heaters, front gate motors, and a newer septic pump motor, etc.  Other exterior features include the covered front porch, storage options, and a spray foam insulated Horse Barn with flex rooms.  We invite you to come see for yourself!  Don't miss the opportunity to make this pristine Texas retreat your own!
